{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.1","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:1","prev_osis_id":"Heb.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. (1 Ch 23:13. H\u00e9 8:3.) (H\u00e9 2:17, 18; 4:15; 7:26-28. Ps 110:4.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>En effet, tout souverain sacrificateur pris du milieu des hommes est \u00e9tabli pour les hommes dans le service de Dieu, afin de pr\u00e9senter des offrandes et des sacrifices pour les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.4.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.2","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:2","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il peut \u00eatre indulgent pour les ignorants et les \u00e9gar\u00e9s, puisque la faiblesse est aussi son partage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.3","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:3","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et c\u2019est \u00e0 cause de cette faiblesse qu\u2019il doit offrir des sacrifices pour ses propres p\u00e9ch\u00e9s, comme pour ceux du peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.4","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:4","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Nul ne s\u2019attribue cette dignit\u00e9, s\u2019il n\u2019est appel\u00e9 de Dieu, comme le fut Aaron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.5","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:5","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et Christ ne s\u2019est pas non plus attribu\u00e9 la gloire de devenir souverain sacrificateur, mais il la tient de celui qui lui a dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Tu es mon Fils,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">je t\u2019ai engendr\u00e9 aujourd\u2019hui!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.6","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:6","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Comme il dit encore ailleurs:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Tu es sacrificateur pour toujours,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">selon l\u2019ordre de Melchis\u00e9dek.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.7","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:7","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\n    C\u2019est lui qui, dans les jours de sa chair, ayant pr\u00e9sent\u00e9 avec de grands cris et avec larmes des pri\u00e8res et des supplications \u00e0 celui qui pouvait le sauver de la mort, et ayant \u00e9t\u00e9 exauc\u00e9 \u00e0 cause de sa pi\u00e9t\u00e9, a appris,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.8","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:8","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>bien qu\u2019il f\u00fbt Fils, l\u2019ob\u00e9issance par les choses qu\u2019il a souffertes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.9","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:9","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>et qui, apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 \u00e9lev\u00e9 \u00e0 la perfection, est devenu pour tous ceux qui lui ob\u00e9issent l\u2019auteur d\u2019un salut \u00e9ternel,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.10","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:10","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Dieu l\u2019ayant d\u00e9clar\u00e9 souverain sacrificateur selon l\u2019ordre de Melchis\u00e9dek.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.11","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:11","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-14: cf. 1 Co 3:1-3.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Nous avons beaucoup \u00e0 dire l\u00e0-dessus, et des choses difficiles \u00e0 expliquer, parce que vous \u00eates devenus lents \u00e0 comprendre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.12","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:12","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Vous, en effet, qui depuis longtemps devriez \u00eatre des ma\u00eetres, vous avez encore besoin qu\u2019on vous enseigne les premiers rudiments des oracles de Dieu, vous en \u00eates venus \u00e0 avoir besoin de lait et non d\u2019une nourriture solide.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.13","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:13","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Or, quiconque en est au lait n\u2019a pas l\u2019exp\u00e9rience de la parole de justice; car il est un enfant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.14","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 5:14","prev_osis_id":"Heb.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.006.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mais la nourriture solide est pour les hommes faits, pour ceux dont le jugement est exerc\u00e9 par l\u2019usage \u00e0 discerner ce qui est bien et ce qui est mal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.6.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.6.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.5.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb8db7546.66035238');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8db7546.66035238\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb8db7546.66035238","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb8db7546.66035238'); }","fums_noscript":